                        <interp inst="t18481218-name-174" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS MAY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, S</hi> 31). I took the prisoner, and have the two sixpences.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
